\begin_layout Plain Layout
Charles et al themselves ignore housing expenses - despite its clear visibility-
 because of the known housing differences in the US between black and white
 social groups
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "CharlesHurstRace"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "CharlesHurstRace"

\end_inset

 (See Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
